text: Anand Dabak is an electrical engineer with Texas Instruments. He was named a Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2014 for his contributions to wireless and power-line communications. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:21st-century American engineers Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
